releases.model_desc_long: Low Power Sub System IOSF2OCP Bridge in Intel AlderLake PCH. Consists of multiple instances of LPSS SPI controller, I2C Controller and HSUART Controller to provide configurable set of external serial I/O ports supporting industry-standard I/O protocols. All the slices connected to the OCP fabric are scalable. ADL-P consist of 7 instances of HSUART Controller, 8 instances of I2C Controller and 7 instances of SPI Controller.
